title: Armorines v2 [Acclaim]
description: Take the finest marines, suit them up in nuclear-powered armor, and you have created the world's ultimate military defense: The Armorines. Set to coincide with the release of the Acclaim video game (Armorines: Project S.W.A.R.M), Armorines Volume II tells the story of Sergeant Anthony Lewis, Myra Lane, Michelle Sirot, and Tork, an unlikely team of soldiers chosen to wear technology derived from the X-O Manowar armor and save the world from the invasion of alien bugs. From the snow swept wastelands of Siberia to the dark jungles of Brazil, this series launches a new era in armored warfare full of fast-paced action, high-tech weaponry, and a hideous form of evil set on world domination.
